# OpenDigital Twin Builder — v5 Final Pack

OpenDigital Twin Builder is an open-source, self-hostable toolkit for creating interoperable digital twins of connected physical assets such as beehives, drones, fabrication equipment and environmental sensors.

## Included
- NLnet form answers
- budget note
- technical attachment
- architecture notes
- landing page copy
- GitHub-ready repo scaffold
- Docker Compose setup
- MQTT demo publisher
- seed data script

## Prototype scope
- tenant-aware architecture
- JWT login
- asset registration
- MQTT telemetry ingestion
- rule-based alert generation
- dashboard-ready API
- self-hosted deployment
